title: All the Fake News That's Fit to Print | Common Sense Central | News/Talk 1130 WISN
text:
All the Fake News That's Fit to Print posted by Dan O'Donnell - 
Dan O'Donnell runs down The Federalist's list of fake news stories the mainstream press has run since the election. Common Sense Central is edited by WISN's Dan O'Donnell. A two-time winner of broadcasting's prestigious National Edward R. Murrow Award, Dan provides unique conservative commentary and analysis of stories that the mainstream media often overlooks. Agree with a story? Disagree? Sound off in the comments section of each story and keep the conversation going on Facebook and Twitter! Contact
